THE MASTER SUITE IS WELL DRESSED WITH TREY CEILINGS, SAFE ROOM & A FINELY APPOINTED BATH. ADDITIONAL FEATURES INCLUDE: HOME AUDIO SYSTEM, 3 ZONE HVAC & NEW GARAGE DOOR.
